                        <h4 class="itemtitle">
                            <a href="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/_JLBij8bAmU/">歷史首個BT種子仍運作   Fan made 版 《The Matrix》已 18 歲</a>
                        </h4>
                        <h5 class="itemposttime">
                            <span>Posted:</span>Fri, 17 Sep 2021 15:14:46 +0000
                        </h5>
                        <div class="itemcontent" name="decodeable"><p class="p1">在尚未出現網上大型串流平台和遊戲主機破解盛行的時候，人們想免費睇劇集、電影，和遊玩破解版遊戲都會選擇用 BitTorrent（後稱 BT）進行下載。時至今日，人們都願意付費看正版影片和玩正版遊戲，就算想看免費影片都會去搜尋線上看。 BT 的使用者就變得少之又少， BT 種子亦會隨着使用者減少而消亡。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1060416" src="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/MV5BY2I4YzE5MTctYzgxNy00ODBlLTg5MTItYjBjOTllOWEwYjA3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjEwNDgzMDA@._V1_-389x580.jpg" alt="" width="389" height="580" srcset="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/MV5BY2I4YzE5MTctYzgxNy00ODBlLTg5MTItYjBjOTllOWEwYjA3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjEwNDgzMDA@._V1_-389x580.jpg 389w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/MV5BY2I4YzE5MTctYzgxNy00ODBlLTg5MTItYjBjOTllOWEwYjA3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjEwNDgzMDA@._V1_.jpg 431w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 389px" /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p class="p1">在 BT 文化息微的時代，史上首個 BT 種子《The Fanimatrix：Run Program》被發現仍可使用。這部短片製作於2003年，是由《<span class="s1">THE MATRIX</span>》（廿二世紀殺人網絡）的 Fans 製作，只憑800元紐幣在9日內完成製作。在成本受限的情況下，再加上當時沒有 YouTube 這個發布平台，《The Fanimatrix》團隊就看中了運用 P2P 技術的 BT 將短片發布，結果發布第一個星期就有大約 7 萬的下載量，在那個年代可說是相當成功。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1060412" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/下載-4.png" alt="" width="200" height="216" /></p><p class="p1" style="text-align: center;"><span class="s1">▲BT </span>是以<span class="s1"> P2P</span>（<span class="s1">peer-to-peer</span>）協定， 用在對等網絡中檔案分享的網絡協定程式。下載同一檔案的人越多，下載該檔案的速度就越快。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1060414" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/image-694x345.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="345" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/image-694x345.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/image-1280x637.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/image-768x382.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/image-1536x764.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/image.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p class="p3">隨著日前《<span class="s1">THE MATRIX 4: Resurrections</span>》的預告釋出，《<span class="s1">The Fanimatrix</span>》亦重新得到網民的關注，而當初在<span class="s1"> BT </span>推出至今已相隔<span class="s1"> 18 </span>年，種子仍然處於可使用狀態實在十分厲害。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p class="p1">資料來源：<a href="https://www.newshub.co.nz/home/technology/2021/09/nz-short-film-the-fanimatrix-the-world-s-oldest-active-torrent-turns-18.html">Newshub</a></p><p class="p1">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s1">unwire.hk Mewe </span><span class="s2">專頁</span><span class="s1"> : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk?fbclid=IwAR3AQOoMxB8P43yFdxzMCeQwO_eHGODMCuisPM_kL8SE2Gvz3NqfHEQPsbk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></span></p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/17/the-fanimatrix-bittorrent-matrix/fun-tech/">歷史首個BT種子仍運作   Fan made 版 《The Matrix》已 18 歲</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk">香港 unwire.hk 玩生活．樂科技</a>.</p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=_JLBij8bAmU:pit1tCMbPaQ:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=_JLBij8bAmU:pit1tCMbPaQ:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/_JLBij8bAmU" height="1" width="1" alt=""/></div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="regularitem">
                        <h4 class="itemtitle">
                            <a href="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/CRAwqpqurwg/">Razer 推出電競手指套  專為手遊玩家而設</a>
                        </h4>
                        <h5 class="itemposttime">
                            <span>Posted:</span>Fri, 17 Sep 2021 15:14:01 +0000
                        </h5>
                        <div class="itemcontent" name="decodeable"><p>在玩手機遊戲例如「食雞」類射擊遊戲或者是 《傳說對決》、《王者榮耀》、《激鬥峽谷》等即時戰略遊戲的時候就需要用到手指進行大量的精準操作，難免有時都會因為手汗太多或者是手機螢幕太滑而導致操作失誤。電競設備大廠 Razer 關注到這個問題，推出了電競手指套—— Razer Gaming Finger Sleeve 這個新配件。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/https___hybrismediaprod.blob_.core_.windows.net_sys-master-phoenix-images-container_h8b_h30_9239168778270_14-Sep-gaming-finger-sleeve-1500x1000-2-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1061229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/https___hybrismediaprod.blob_.core_.windows.net_sys-master-phoenix-images-container_h8b_h30_9239168778270_14-Sep-gaming-finger-sleeve-1500x1000-2-1-694x435.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="435" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/https___hybrismediaprod.blob_.core_.windows.net_sys-master-phoenix-images-container_h8b_h30_9239168778270_14-Sep-gaming-finger-sleeve-1500x1000-2-1-694x435.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/https___hybrismediaprod.blob_.core_.windows.net_sys-master-phoenix-images-container_h8b_h30_9239168778270_14-Sep-gaming-finger-sleeve-1500x1000-2-1-768x482.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/https___hybrismediaprod.blob_.core_.windows.net_sys-master-phoenix-images-container_h8b_h30_9239168778270_14-Sep-gaming-finger-sleeve-1500x1000-2-1.jpg 789w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1060629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/https___hybrismediaprod.blob_.core_.windows.net_sys-master-phoenix-images-container_h3a_h31_9239168712734_14-Sep-gaming-finger-sleeve-1500x1000-3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/https___hybrismediaprod.blob_.core_.windows.net_sys-master-phoenix-images-container_h3a_h31_9239168712734_14-Sep-gaming-finger-sleeve-1500x1000-3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/https___hybrismediaprod.blob_.core_.windows.net_sys-master-phoenix-images-container_h3a_h31_9239168712734_14-Sep-gaming-finger-sleeve-1500x1000-3-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/https___hybrismediaprod.blob_.core_.windows.net_sys-master-phoenix-images-container_h3a_h31_9239168712734_14-Sep-gaming-finger-sleeve-1500x1000-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/https___hybrismediaprod.blob_.core_.windows.net_sys-master-phoenix-images-container_h3a_h31_9239168712734_14-Sep-gaming-finger-sleeve-1500x1000-3.jpg 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Razer Gaming Finger Sleeve 以一套兩隻形式販售，售價為 9.99 美元（大約為 78 港元）。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Razer Gaming Finger Sleeve 聲稱能防止手指打滑，讓手指在玩手機遊戲時保持乾燥。這個配件採用了平滑的高靈敏度布料、輕便透氣，可在減少摩擦的同時增強指尖觸控螢幕時的靈敏性和反應速度。手指套尺寸為 21 mm x 45 mm，厚度大約為 0.8 mm，適用於不同尺寸的手指，手指套還可以清洗後重新使用。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p class="p1">資料來源：<a href="https://www.razer.com/gear-accessories/razer-gaming-finger-sleeve/RC81-03970100-R3M1">Razer</a></p><p class="p1">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s1">unwire.hk Mewe </span><span class="s2">專頁</span><span class="s1"> : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk?fbclid=IwAR3AQOoMxB8P43yFdxzMCeQwO_eHGODMCuisPM_kL8SE2Gvz3NqfHEQPsbk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/17/razer-gaming-finger-sleeve/game-channel/">Razer 推出電競手指套  專為手遊玩家而設</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk">香港 unwire.hk 玩生活．樂科技</a>.</p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=CRAwqpqurwg:X_jDu0eylYA:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=CRAwqpqurwg:X_jDu0eylYA:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/CRAwqpqurwg" height="1" width="1" alt=""/></div>
