                        </h4>
                        <h5 class="itemposttime">
                            <span>Posted:</span>Fri, 17 Sep 2021 15:09:41 +0000
                        </h5>
                        <div class="itemcontent" name="decodeable"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Microsoft 去年年底曾預告將推動用戶使用無密碼存取，當時稱已有 1.5 億用戶以 Windows Hello 或 Authenticator App 等無密碼的登入方式來登入 Azure Active Directory。Microsoft 本週就宣佈，將在最近幾個禮拜內讓所有 Microsoft 賬號以免密碼的方式登入。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1060614" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Password-removed-694x331.png" alt="" width="694" height="331" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Password-removed-694x331.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Password-removed.png 698w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Microsoft 在本月 15 日表示，現時用戶均可利用無密碼方式，例如指紋等生物辨識技術 Windows Hello、Microsoft Authenticator 手機 App、FIDO 硬體金鑰以及手機短訊或郵件寄發的驗證碼登入帳號。當中所涵蓋的服務包括 Microsoft 365、Teams、Outlook、OneDrive、Family Safety App 及 Microsoft Edge 等。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1060615" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Picture3-694x145.png" alt="" width="694" height="145" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Picture3-694x145.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Picture3-768x160.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Picture3.png 1098w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Microsoft 副總裁 Vasu Jakkal 指出，這項功能將在未來幾個星期內推向所有用戶，表示透過無密碼登入，在很大程度上可免於黑客以釣魚信件或網站騙取用戶帳密事件。 Jakkal 亦表示，現時 Microsoft 員工以無密碼登入公司賬號的比例已將近 100%。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/security/blog/2021/09/15/the-passwordless-future-is-here-for-your-microsoft-account/">Microsoft</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwire</span></a></p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/17/microsoft-accounts-can-now-go-fully-passwordless/life-tech/">Microsoft 賬戶可免密碼登入  涵蓋 Microsoft 365、Outlook、OneDrive</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk">香港 unwire.hk 玩生活．樂科技</a>.</p><div class="feedflare">
