                        <h4 class="itemtitle">
                            <a href="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/k3v9MP6gVsk/">SpaceX 首次商業載人任務順利升空 「太空素人」將於三日後返回地球</a>
                        </h4>
                        <h5 class="itemposttime">
                            <span>Posted:</span>Fri, 17 Sep 2021 15:09:35 +0000
                        </h5>
                        <div class="itemcontent" name="decodeable"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">太空探索技術公司（SpaceX）首個太空旅行團於今日（16日）上午 8 時左右順利升空並成功進入軌道。此項太空任務 Inspiration4 由四名 「太空素人」組成，預計將於三天後返回地球。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">本次的太空任務共有四位完全非官方機構、無太空飛行經驗的機組人員，是由美國支付公司「Shift4 Payments」行政總裁 Jared Isaacman 發起，他亦同時擔任四位「太空素人」中的指揮官。另外三位成員分別為醫務人員 Hayley Arceneaux、地質學家和科學通訊員 Sian Proctor 以及美國退役空軍、航空機械工程師Chris Sembroski。為本次任務他們進行了長達半年的訓練，除身體訓練及惡補基本知識外，同時間亦進行多次的模擬器訓練，以了解如何應對太空中的各種臨時狀況。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1060708" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-2-694x251.png" alt="" width="694" height="251" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-2-694x251.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-2-1280x463.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-2-768x278.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-2-1536x556.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-2-2048x741.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-2.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Inspiration4  所發射的火箭是 Falcon 9，太空艙則是已出過兩次任務的 Endeavour 。此太空艙負責了過往 Demo-2 和 Crew-2 的任務，是次則是其第三次升空。因飛船並沒有準備與國際太空站進行對接，因此在發射時間和軌道上較為自由。他們會到達最高 540 公里左右的軌道，並進行少量的科研工作。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1060709" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-3-694x377.png" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-3-694x377.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-3-1280x695.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-3-768x417.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-3-1536x834.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-3-2048x1112.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-3.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1060710" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-6-694x385.png" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-6-694x385.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-6-1280x710.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-6-768x426.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-6-1536x852.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-6-2048x1136.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/05p7pBsjdyaEFK9IE2G7ePg-6.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">另與其他太空旅行公司如 Virgin Galactic、Blue Origin 早前啟動的太空旅遊服務相比，以往的太空旅行只持續約 10-90 分鐘，而 Inspiration4 停留在太空的時間則長達3日，是在太空停留時間最長的一次太空飛行任務。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_58287"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332"  src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3pv01sSq44w?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://au.pcmag.com/news/89509/how-to-watch-inspiration-4-blast-off-for-the-first-all-civilian-orbital-space-flight">PC Mag</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwire</span></a></p><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/17/inspiration-4-successfully-blasts-off-for-the-first-all-civilian-orbital-space-flight/life-tech/">SpaceX 首次商業載人任務順利升空 「太空素人」將於三日後返回地球</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://unwire.hk">香港 unwire.hk 玩生活．樂科技</a>.</p><div class="feedflare">
